  "source": "books_masroka/egypt_civilization/ancient_egypt_articles_on_how_ancient_egypt_was_preserved_by_the_outside_world/105656-Article Text-282504-1-10-20250425-2.pdf",
  "title": "egypt_civilization/ancient_egypt_articles_on_how_ancient_egypt_was_preserved_by_the_outside_world_105656-Article Text-282504-1-10-20250425-2",
